se.miun.itm.input.model

Class Ranges

  • java.lang.Object
    • se.miun.itm.input.model.Ranges

  • public class Ranges
extends java.lang.Object
    Each numeric parameter (implicitly) defines a range of valid values. This range information is all available via its instance of the ranges class.
    Author:
    Felix Dobslaw
